# 1. software version                                                *
# 2. proc_card          : code generation info including model       *
# 3. param_card         : model primary parameters in the LH format  *
# 4. run_card           : running parameters (collider and cuts)     *
# 5. pythia_card        : present only if pythia has been run        *
